name: Superball
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: super ball
des:
Control the ball with the power of your words! But don't get too close to the obstacles, because they could end your game.
Just say "left" or "right". 

This game was specifically designed for the interaction with Alexa. Voice processing delay is also a part of the game and serves as an extra challenge.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
